
  # Router (Built-in HTTP router)
    + Responsible for translating incoming HTTP request into `Action`
    + Routes are specified in routes file
      - ***`conf/routes`
      - routes file is compiled (So we will get compilation error directly in browser)
    + Event
      - A HTTP request is considered as event by MVC framework
      - ***Contains 2 pieces of information
        . `Request path` & `Query string` (Example: /clients/1542)
        . HTTP method (GET, POST, ...)
        
  # Reference
    + https://www.playframework.com/documentation/2.6.x/ScalaRouting#The-built-in-HTTP-router
    
      
    
  